Some people think that the Earth is flat.  How they would think that Earth is flat I don't know.  Some people think that the earth is flat, like a sheet of glass with known raised areas.  Since they think that they also think that Mt. Everest does not exist.
Only around two thirds of the population believe that the earth is round.  Which is kind of crazy seeing that it was proved that the earth was round a long time ago.  We know that the earth is round because if there was a boat going out to sea you would be able to see it if the earth was flat.  But because the earth is round you can't see it no matter how far out it goes it will go past/into the horizon line so we can't see it.  Also another reason the earth his round is because there are shadows. During a lunar eclipse, the Earth passes between the moon and the sun. When that happens, the sun projects Earth’s shadow onto the moon. When this happens, you can actually see the Earth’s shadow if you look up at the moon. If you do this, you’ll see that there is a round shadow, not a flat one.
